query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(s1 t1 tq1 q1) */ select count(account.display_name)
from tag AS t1
inner join site AS s1
on t1.site_id = s1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('magento-1.6',
'404',
'tabs',
'mysql',
'sales',
'cms-block',
'soap',
'full-page-cache',
'email') AND s1.site_name = 'magento'
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on tq1.tag_id = t1.id AND tq1.site_id = s1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on tq1.question_id = q1.id AND q1.site_id = s1.site_id AND q1.score > 11 AND q1.view_count < 2069
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.site_id = u1.site_id
inner join account AS account
on account.id = u1.account_id
inner join comment AS c1
on c1.site_id = q1.site_id AND c1.post_id = q1.id;
